name: Calculator
tagline: Simple calculator app with vanilla JavaScript
body:
#Simple Calculator App Demo

This calculator application is made as a demonstration of Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) principles. It also demonstrates the usage of Principle of Least Privilege. 

Please feel free to contribute any code  to improve the UX of this calculator.

Thanks!
